    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nS_1 = \\int_{0}^{8} (-0,125x^2 + x)dx = \\left[-\\frac{0,125}{3}x^3 + \\frac{x^2}{2}\\right]_{0}^{8} = \\frac{32}{3} \\text{ (dvdt)}.\n$$"
